data.description: Check out this, almost 3,000SF, home in West El Paso! Conveniently located off I-10W and Helen of Troy, an area known for its shopping, dining, entertainment and fitness options. This home has 4 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms, a loft, 2 living rooms and 2 dining areas. It has 2 primary bedrooms (1 upstairs and 1 downstairs) with luxuries such as, outdoor patio access, spacious walk-in closets with built-in shelving and large en-suite bathrooms equipped with dual vanity sinks, oversized garden bathtubs and stand-alone showers. The kitchen is a central part of any home, and this one is definitely a gathering place with a large island and open design, ensures that the kitchen is both functional and aesthetically pleasing. The roof of the house was fully replaced on 9/15/23, and it comes with a transferrable warranty. Seller will contribute 2% of Purchase Price towards the buyer's closing costs! VA Assumable Loan Option at ~4.5%!
